oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unidentified woman
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Ambrotype of unidentified woman in her twenties wearing a dark dress with lace collar, and dark lace fingerless gloves. The woman's dark hair is parted in the middle and slicked back. Her necklace and belt have been tinted with gold leaf. The photograph was found among items from the Talley family estate.
